title: The Legend of the Demon God
description: The Legend of the Demon God Manhua Thousands of years ago, the immortal clan and demon clan were battling for the universe. To defend the peace and justice, the immortal clan created a mysterious legendary fighter, who blew himself up into thousands of pieces, floating in the world. And Lu Xiaofei inherit a piece of the fighter. Demon God The Legend of the Demon God 解离妖圣 解離妖聖
alternative_titles: The Legend of the Demon God
